{"article_id":"iG27ZYlnpfZOHAXo","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Do You Support Background Checks on Gun Buyers ?","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Vote in Urgent Poll","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Do You Support Background Checks on Gun Buyers ?","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Vote in Urgent Poll","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"Despite signs of bipartisanship on Capitol Hill in recent days ,","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"relations between the two parties remain tense","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"and Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell seems ready to push back on votes","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"testing support for controversial gun and immigration proposals.","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"McConnell and other top Republicans are opposed to a plan","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"crafted by Democratic Sen. Joe Manchin of West Virginia and GOP Sen. Pat Toomey of Pennsylvania","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"to expand background checks on the sale of firearms","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and are trying to devise amendments","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"to kill the agreement ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Politico reports .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Republican Sen. Chuck Grassley of Iowa is drafting an alternative gun bill ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and McConnell could try to force votes","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"on allowing guns in federal buildings and national parks ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"the news publication said.","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"While Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid needs 60 votes","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"to move the Manchin-Toomey plan forward ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"their apparent goal is to force Democrats in largely Republican states","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"who are up for re-election in 2014","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"to pressure Reid to retract the bill ,","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"according to the publication.","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"it ' s an open question as to whether or not we have the votes , \"","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Toomey said Sunday on CNN ' s \" State of the Union , \"","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"it ' s going to be close. \"","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"So far , only four out of 45 Senate Republicans ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"including Toomey , Mark Kirk of Illinois , Susan Collins of Maine , and John McCain of Arizona ,","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"are reportedly set to support the bipartisan proposal ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"reported The Hill ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"which surveyed the Senate mood .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"There are a dozen other Republicans","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"who voted for a motion","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"to proceed on the gun control bill last week ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"including Sens . Kelly Ayotte of New Hampshire ; Jeff Flake of Arizona ; Saxby Chambliss and Johnny Isakson of Georgia ; Roger Wicker of Mississippi ; and Dean Heller of Nevada ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"The Hill found in its survey.","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Flake said","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"he is reviewing the bill .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Heller ' s office told The Hill","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"the senator \" will not support any plan","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"that creates a federal gun registry. \"","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Corker , meanwhile , is reviewing the bill ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"according to The Tennessean.","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Chambliss said","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"he opposes it .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Wicker said on C-SPAN Monday morning","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"that he is opposed to the Manchin-Toomey amendment.","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"To pass Manchin-Toomey ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"at least five Republicans must back it .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Fifty-five senators caucus with the Democrats ,","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"but not all are sure bets","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"to embrace the background check legislation.","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"And immigration may be just as tough .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"While a bipartisan group of eight senators is working on legislation","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"that could reach the floor of the upper chamber this summer ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"several GOP lawmakers have signaled","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"they intend to fight it","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"because it would establish a pathway to citizenship for 11 million immigrants","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"who came here illegally.","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Sen . Jeff Session of Alabama , the senior Republican on the Judiciary Committee , said on \" Fox News Sunday \"","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"he is opposed to the legislation","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"because it \" will give amnesty now ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"legalize everyone","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"that ' s here effectively today. \"","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Making things even more difficult is McConnell ' s apparent refusal","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"to work with Reid anymore on fashioning a possible \" grand bargain \" on budget and tax issues ,","depth":4},{"id":70,"text":"Politico also reported .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":141,"left":74,"right":140,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":72,"right":73,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":137,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":122,"right":136,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":122,"left":77,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":4,"right":76,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":5,"right":75,"rel